        "product_description": {
            "value": "Keep your suede and Gore-Tex footwear looking like new with the GEAR AID Revivex Suede Shoe Cleaner and Conditioning Kit. This complete restoration set includes everything you need to clean, protect, and refresh your favorite sneakers and boots. The kit features a specialized soap to gently lift away dirt and grime, a water repellent spray that safeguards suede and Gore-Tex fabrics from moisture and stains, a cleaning brush to remove embedded dirt and revive the nap, and an eraser to reduce unsightly scuffs and marks. Ideal for maintaining suede, nubuck, and technical fabrics, this 2-pack ensures you always have the tools on hand to extend the life and appearance of your footwear. Trust GEAR AID to help you restore and protect the shoes you love.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
            "model": "claude-opus-4-8"
        },
